{"tid":644531,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動畫《進擊的巨人 第三季》公開新視覺圖及首段宣傳影片","createTime":"2018-04-27T09:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T15:26:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d5043fcb449bc910856162ad832f821b19442c46","tid":644531,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"自從超大型巨人出現，人類的和平與幻想被打破的那天開始，艾倫&middot;耶格爾無盡戰鬥的日子就未曾中斷&hellip;&hellip;。毫無抵抗之力，眼睜睜看着母親成為巨人的餌食，發誓將巨人一個不剩地從世上驅逐的艾倫。但，在殘酷戰鬥的途中，他自己也變成了巨人的姿態&mdash;&mdash;。為了奪回人類的自由而驅使巨人之力的艾倫，在席納之牆的史托黑斯區與「女巨人」交鋒。這場巨人之間的激烈戰鬥，由艾倫艱難地取得了勝利。即使如此，艾倫以及人類也沒有休息的時間。下一場戰鬥已經宣告開幕。面對逼近羅塞之牆的大群巨人，人類將如何對敵！？<br />\n<br />\n以諫山創擔任原著漫畫改編，動畫《進擊的巨人》預定推出的第三季電視動畫，預定今年 7 月開始播映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，官方近日公開了新視覺圖與首段宣傳影片。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/49/845298fca86c40d0495a1d795510o6d5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F49%2F845298fca86c40d0495a1d795510o6d5.JPG&h=ba3fdca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/1/161951.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F1%2F161951.html&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65liS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ca3cbd97\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/1/161951.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"3c37f4c6a957ac7ec1f5f26d56c5e6c56c47bdcb","tid":644531,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EHzBhrncmac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEHzBhrncmac&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65liS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9460cedc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EHzBhrncmac</a>"},{"pid":"1aa9ab58a2091c9385f8918ae7080fd34cd2ae36","